title: Assassination Classroom (As of 4-1-16)
description:
Ansatsu Kyoushitsu/Assassination Classroom
One of my favorite manga series.

This gives you Chapters 1-180.5. It is complete currently as it finished
at 180 Chapters and 180.5 was an extra added.

The manga can be found online at mangahere.co
This is for if you want the complete series for offline viewing.
Please support the official release!
